# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) for local `just wrangler-dev`.
# Only needed to actually deliver a feedback email in local dev — omit it and
# the Worker exercises the Resend non-2xx (502) error path instead.
#
# Get a key at https://resend.com (API Keys). For a real local send you also
# need the feedback.veilkeepergame.com sending domain verified in Resend.
RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_key_here
